PN,31901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FVolunteers have cleaned more than a
OL,7,Ftonne of fly-tipped waste from a
OL,8,Fbeauty spot in the Rhonda Valley, as
OL,9,FITV News Wales Reporter Rhys Williams
OL,10,Fexplains
OL,12,FFly-tipping and illegal waste disposal
OL,13,Fhas evolved into a large-scale
OL,14,Fcriminal industry that is harming
OL,15,Frural communities across the UK and
OL,16,Fcosting the economy millions of pounds
OL,17,Feach year, according to a new report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FThe report - by the National Rural
OL,7,FCrime Network (NRCN) and Future
OL,8,FCountryside - calls on the government
OL,9,Fto introduce a single national system
OL,10,Fwhere people can report fly-tipping
OL,11,Fand waste crimes.
OL,13,FIt comes after volunteers cleaned more
OL,14,Fthan a tonne of waste, which had been
OL,15,Ffly-tipped in a beauty spot in the
OL,16,FRhonda Valley. It had been dumped down
OL,17,Fthe side of a mountain and teams
OL,18,Fneeded to use ropes in a 12 hour
OL,19,Foperation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FIncidents have soared across the
OL,7,Fcountry in recent years, with
OL,8,Forganised waste crime groups growing
OL,9,Fincreasingly sophisticated and massive
OL,10,Fillegal dumps in protected areas
OL,11,Fsparking public outrage.
OL,13,FOfficial figures also showed fly-
OL,14,Ftipping on public land increased by 9%
OL,15,Flast year to new highs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FHowever, the rural groups, which bring
OL,7,Ftogether organisations such as the
OL,8,FNational Farmers' Union, Crimestoppers
OL,9,Fand the Countryside Alliance, say the
OL,10,Ftrue scale of the problem is likely to
OL,11,Fbe far greater.
OL,13,FThat is because incidents on private
OL,14,Fland, large-scale illegal dumping
OL,15,Fhandled by the Environment Agency and
OL,16,Fmany unreported cases are excluded
OL,17,Ffrom the national data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FWhile the government has recently
OL,7,Funveiled a string of reforms to tackle
OL,8,Fwaste crime under a national action
OL,9,Fplan, the campaigners are calling on
OL,10,Fministers, regulators, police forces,
OL,11,Flocal authorities and the Environment
OL,12,FAgency to work together to deliver a
OL,13,Fmore co-ordinated and effective
OL,14,Fnational response.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FAhead of the report launch at the
OL,7,FFuture Countryside conference on
OL,8,FTuesday, the groups said ministers
OL,9,Fshould introduce a single reporting
OL,10,Froute for all fly-tipping incidents,
OL,11,Fwhich they say the government has
OL,12,Fexpressly declined to do.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
