FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FThey also want to see a comprehensive
OL,7,Fnational dataset that covers all fly-
OL,8,Ftipping and waste crime incidents,
OL,9,Fincluding those on private land,
OL,10,Fallowing the scale of the problem and
OL,11,Fthe response to be tracked accurately
OL,12,Fyear-on-year.
OL,14,FA new waste crime (prevention) act
OL,15,Fshould be tabled to bring together a
OL,16,Frange of reforms under a single
OL,17,Flegislative framework, the
OL,18,Forganisations added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FAnd ministers must take action to
OL,7,Fshift the responsibility for the costs
OL,8,Fof fly-tipping incidents on private
OL,9,Fland from landowners to local
OL,10,Fauthorities, they said.
OL,12,FThis measure that was recently put
OL,13,Fforward in the House of Lords resulted
OL,14,Fin a Government defeat, before it was
OL,15,Foverturned in the Commons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
