FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,FNRCN chairman Tim Passmore said:
OL,7,F"Waste crime and fly-tipping is not
OL,8,Flow-level nuisance offending ` it is
OL,9,Fserious, organised criminality that is
OL,10,Fdamaging our environment, hitting
OL,11,Frural communities hard and leaving
OL,12,Finnocent victims to foot the bill.
OL,14,F"Criminals know the risks are low and
OL,15,Fthe rewards are high. That has to
OL,16,Fchange.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,F"We need tougher enforcement, sharper
OL,7,Faccountability and a system that
OL,8,Ffinally treats waste crime and fly-
OL,9,Ftipping with the seriousness it
OL,10,Fdeserves."
OL,12,FJulian Glover, co-founder of Future
OL,13,FCountryside, said: "Fly-tipping is no
OL,14,Flonger a simple environmental nuisance.
OL,16,F"It has become a serious criminal
OL,17,Fenterprise which blights communities,
OL,18,Fharms nature and places victims under
OL,19,Funacceptable financial pressure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]uD@TOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,F"All too often, rural communities are
OL,7,Fexpected to shoulder the costs while
OL,8,Foffenders operate with impunity."
OL,10,FAn Environment Department (Defra)
OL,11,Fspokesperson said: "Waste criminals
OL,12,Fwho blight our countryside and
OL,13,Fundermine our rural way of life have
OL,14,Fgone unpunished for too long.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]sD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
