OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780416668
OL,3,CIntroduce a single national system to
OL,4,Creport fly-tipping, rural groups urge
OL,6,F"This Government is ramping up efforts
OL,7,Fand tackling organised crime head on `
OL,8,Fwe have increased the Environment
OL,9,FAgency's enforcement budget to #15.6
OL,10,Fmillion, bolstered the joint unit for
OL,11,Fwaste crime and our waste crime action
OL,12,Fplan sets out how we are cracking down
OL,13,Fon those responsible.
OL,15,F"We continue to work closely with
OL,16,Flandowners to promote good practice on
OL,17,Ffly-tipping prevention alongside
OL,18,Fsupporting local authorities and
OL,19,Fpolice to investigate, seize and crush
OL,20,Fvehicles used to illegally dump waste."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
